'''Earl''' is a patient who came into the clinic.

==History==
Earl had redness in his urine and came into the clinic worried he had cancer because he thought it was blood. Alex ran tests and told Earl he was having a known reaction to the beets he'd eaten which caused the pigment to pass through his body.
